| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1326 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e66c7129-4554-5c5d-aae3-351257b96ee5"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
